 <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fbe5b4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub28.ezboard.com/urahan.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Rahan</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_lightning.gif BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 196<br> <font color=#993300>(6/7/01 11:03:45 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Naggy and Vox buffing.</span><hr size=1> I agree with Barge, usually the problems is the lack of resist gear.....<br>
