Bah just bring a shaman to focus and a cleric to aegolism and a ench to Vision of grandeur, you cant fail ;) <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fed995><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub28.ezboard.com/ureshu.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Reshu</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 33<br> <font color=#993300>(6/7/01 3:34:52 pm)</font><br>     <br>Community Supporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Naggy and Vox buffing.</span><hr size=1> Shaman to focus, cleric to aego, chanter to visions, and a pally to.. uh.. hrm.. a pally to um.. hmmm. pally to.. geeze.. why is this so tough.. oh yeah.. pally to make everyone laugh before they trudge off into battle :)<br>
